### VLab — VMware SOAP API Tests
### Covers: snapshot (list / create / revert / delete) and linked clone
### Run: npm run dev (port 8800)

@base = http://localhost:8800
@api  = {{base}}/api

@adminEmail    = admin@vlab.com
@adminPassword = admin123

# Update these with real IDs from your vCenter
# vmId:     source VM MoRef  — get from GET /api/vmware/vcenter/vm
# folderId: target folder    — get from GET /api/vmware/vcenter/folder?type=VIRTUAL_MACHINE
@vmId     = vm-427
@folderId = group-v82


###
# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login — admin
POST {{api}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}


###
# ============================================================
# SNAPSHOTS
# ============================================================

### List snapshots of a VM
GET {{api}}/vmware-soap/vcenter/vm/{{vmId}}/snapshots

###

### Create snapshot
# 执行 linked clone 前先用这个为模板 VM 建快照
POST {{api}}/vmware-soap/vcenter/vm/{{vmId}}/snapshots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "base-snapshot",
  "description": "linked clone base"
}

###

### Revert to current snapshot
POST {{api}}/vmware-soap/vcenter/vm/{{vmId}}/snapshots/revert

###

### Remove all snapshots
DELETE {{api}}/vmware-soap/vcenter/vm/{{vmId}}/snapshots


###
# ============================================================
# LINKED CLONE
# ============================================================

### Linked clone — 模板 VM 必须已有快照
POST {{api}}/vmware-soap/vcenter/vm/{{vmId}}/clone
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "student-vm-test-01",
  "folderId": "{{folderId}}"
}
